{"tid":712079,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[經驗討論] 付出最多嗰個點解唔係贏家？","createTime":"2018-06-22T00:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T01:04:49.000Z","uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45aa634252b523f43eed89befade3eb691b0f3db","tid":712079,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:58:50.000Z","msg":"例子 1：<br />\n中學時期，大部分 Band 2 學生都比 Band 1 學生更加努力，補課總時長一定比 Band 1 學生長。<br />\n<br />\n最後入大學率最高嘅反而係 Band 1 學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子 2：<br />\n香港人出名勤力過人，打工仔一向工時長又捱得。反之，美國打工仔工時短又唔捱得。<br />\n<br />\n但美國打工仔嘅人均收入比香港高得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子 3：<br />\n大部份本土窮後代都係好捱得又肯博，而大部分本土二世祖都係又懶又唔捱得。<br />\n<br />\n最後人生贏家當然係二世祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子 4：<br />\n十四億支那人/印度人共同努力，理論上應該會變成世界最強最穩健嘅國度。<br />\n<br />\n而事實上，不論科技、商業、教育、法治，支那同印度都係大大輸俾只有三億人嘅美國/其他人口更少嘅北歐國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人知道點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"aa81474a4217a3db0bb9200d3a2647252f3a24a5","tid":712079,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T01:04:30.000Z","msg":"痴線 中國不嬲都係最大贏家"},{"pid":"8bf672079934173250f20d779bd00b951e598ea4","tid":712079,"uid":147459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T01:04:49.000Z","msg":"因為天賦比努力更加重要，此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}